.ship-notes/CR-onyx-2nd-Claude-Standard-20260412-014426.md:12:Small, surgical, mechanical fix. The math is right, the cascade parity is right, the new test actually exercises the reachable path, and `cargo test render::svdag` + `cargo test wgsl_drift_guard` are both 24/24 and 2/2 green. The one thing the patch leaves on the table is the drift-guard pin parallel to hash-thing-6hd — Important, not a blocker, and correctly filed as a scout follow-up (see Finding 3 below).
